# shadcn/ui Component Library Rules

## Overview
This project uses **shadcn/ui** exclusively for all UI components. Do not create custom UI components or use alternative UI libraries when a shadcn/ui component exists.

## Initial Setup

### First-Time Installation
If shadcn/ui is not initialized in the project, run:

```bash
npx shadcn@latest init
```

This command will:
- Set up the components directory structure
- Configure `components.json`
- Set up Tailwind CSS integration
- Configure path aliases (@/components/ui/*)

